title: Magnolia Jazzband and Topsy Chapman - 2008 - Live At Oslo Concer
description:
Magnolia Jazzband and Topsy Chapman - 2008 - Live At Oslo Concert Hall

This record was made from Magnolia Jazzband's 35th anniversary concert in Oslo Concert Hall, September 8th 2007.

Track list:
1 - Lonesome and Sorry - J. Benny Davis / Con Conrad
2 - Shout, Sister, Shout! - Rosetta Tharpe
3 - I'm Through with Love - Livingstone / Malneck / Khan
4 - St. Louis Blues - W. C. Handy
5 - Muddy Waters - Rose / Richman / Trent
6 - Blue Bells Goodbye - Theodore F. Morse / Edward Madden
7 - Fine and Mellow - Billie Holiday
8 - I Cried for You - Gus Arnheim / Arthur Freed / Abe Lyman
9 - My Man - Pollack Yvain
10 - Down in Honky Tonk Town - Chris Smith / Charles Mc Carron
